            From the Town East Mall to the medical district, we keep Mesquite businesses spotless and professional. Trusted by local Mesquite companies for reliability and excellence.
          </p>
          
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 animate-fade-in delay-100">
            <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-brand-gold text-white rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-brand-gold/90 transition-colors">
              Get Your Free Quote
            </a>
            <a href="tel:817-993-9993" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white border-2 border-brand-gold text-brand-gold rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-brand-gold hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Call Now: (817) 993-9993
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mesquite Business Environment -->
    <section class="py-16">
      <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">
            Mesquite's Trusted Commercial Cleaning Experts
          </h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Mesquite, known for its strong retail presence and growing business community, offers 
                diverse commercial opportunities. From the bustling Town East Mall area to the expanding 
                medical district, your business environment reflects Mesquite's commitment to growth 
                and community service.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-700 mb-6">
                Dream Cleaned understands the unique cleaning challenges of Mesquite businesses. 
                Whether you're in the retail sector, healthcare, or professional services, we 
                provide tailored cleaning solutions that maintain the high standards your customers 
                and employees expect in this dynamic city.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg border-l-4 border-brand-gold self-start">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Mesquite Businesses Choose<br>Dream Cleaned</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                  <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Experience with retail environments</span>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center p-3 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg">
                  <CheckCircle className="h-4 w-4 text-brand-gold mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-700">Knowledge of Mesquite's business districts</span>
